982
01:06:55,030 --> 01:06:56,600
我们死定了
We're dead soon.

983
01:06:57,700 --> 01:06:59,610
你就不能再试试吗
Can you at least try?

984
01:07:01,950 --> 01:07:03,640
巨鹰
Giant hawk.

985
