现在只剩下我和你
It's just me and you.

1015
01:08:48,770 --> 01:08:50,290
我想帮你
And I want to help.

1016
01:08:51,570 --> 01:08:55,560
可你不愿意让我帮你
But I can't if you don't let me.

1017
01:09:01,210 --> 01:09:03,510
我并不是天生的半神
I wasn't born a demigod.

1018
01:09:04,330 --> 01:09:05,650
我的父母都是凡人
I had human parents.

1019
01:09:07,140 --> 01:09:08,340
他们
They...

1020
01:09:09,020 --> 01:09:10,100
他们只是看了一眼
They took one look and...

1021
01:09:11,200 --> 01:09:14,490
就决定要把我扔掉
And decided they did not want me.

1022
01:09:15,910 --> 01:09:17,410
他们把我丢到了海里
They threw me under the sea.

1023
01:09:18,440 --> 01:09:20,930
就像什么事也没发生一样
Like I was nothing.

1024
01:09:23,150 --> 01:09:25,840
不知怎么地，天神们发现了我
Somehow I was found by the Gods.

1025
01:09:26,620 --> 01:09:27,770
还给了我这根鱼钩法杖
They gave me the hook.

1026
01:09:28,980 --> 01:09:31,630
是他们让我成为了毛伊
They made me... Maui.

1027
01:09:33,350 --> 01:09:35,630
之后我回到了人类当中
And back to the humans I went.

1028
01:09:36,540 --> 01:09:39,780
为他们带去了海岛、火种、椰子
I gave them islands, fire, coconuts!

1029
01:09:41,400 --> 01:09:42,700
他们要什么我就给什么
Anything they could ever want.

1030
01:09:44,410 --> 01:09:45,790
你为他们拿了那颗心
You took the heart for them.

1031
01:09:47,500 --> 01:09:49,770
为他们做任何事
You did everything for them.

1032
01:09:51,060 --> 01:09:52,260
只希望能讨好他们
So they'd loved you.

1033
01:09:53,390 --> 01:09:56,050
可他们永远都不满足
It was never enough.

1034
01:10:04,810 --> 01:10:07,550
也许天神发现你是有原因的
Maybe the Gods found you for a reason.

1035
01:10:08,200 --> 01:10:10,820
也许是大海把你带到了他们面前
Maybe the ocean brought you to them.

1036
01:10:11,630 --> 01:10:14,840
因为它觉得你命不该绝
Because it saw someone who is worthy of being saved.

1037
01:10:16,930 --> 01:10:19,740
但是让你成为毛伊的并不是天神
But the Gods aren't the ones who make you Maui.

1038
01:10:21,260 --> 01:10:22,510
而是你自己
You are.

1039
01:10:31,980 --> 01:10:33,510
好了
Okay, okay.

1040
01:10:35,380 --> 01:10:37,370
我也爱你，伙计
I... I love you too, buddy.

1041
01:11:43,470 --> 01:11:44,470
真棒
Yeah!

1042
01:12:08,450 --> 01:12:10,410
下一站，特菲提岛
Next stop, Te Fiti.

1043
01:12:58,010 --> 01:13:01,340
- 看什么？  - 我知道了
- What?  - I figured it out

1044
01:13:01,840 --> 01:13:05,720
其实大海让我拉来那些岛屿
You know the ocean used to love when I pulled up islands.

1045
01:13:05,820 --> 01:13:08,920
是为了让你的祖先们在航海时发现它们
'Cause your ancestors would sail our seas. Find them!

1046
01:13:10,150 --> 01:13:12,490
然后在岛上建立村庄
All those new lands, new villages...

1047
01:13:13,510 --> 01:13:15,280
所有的岛屿和村庄都因为大海而连在一起
It was the water that connected them all.

1048
01:13:16,470 --> 01:13:17,740
如果我是大海
And if I were the ocean

1049
01:13:18,270 --> 01:13:19,990
我也会选择一个
I think I'd be looking for a...

1050
01:13:20,200 --> 01:13:22,170
卷发的酋长女儿
Curly haired, non-princess.

1051
01:13:23,080 --> 01:13:24,500
让一切都从头开始
To start that again.

1052
01:13:25,100 --> 01:13:27,480
你从来没有对我说过
That is literaly the nicest thing

1053
01:13:27,510 --> 01:13:29,330
这么感人的话呢
You've ever said to me.

1054
01:13:30,430 --> 01:13:33,110
也许你应该等到了特菲提岛再说
Probably should've saved it for Te Fiti.

1055
01:13:34,180 --> 01:13:35,670
已经到了
I did.

1056
01:13:38,150 --> 01:13:39,840
莫图鲁尼岛的莫阿娜
Moana of Motunui.

1057
01:13:40,290 --> 01:13:41,410
我想你
I believe.

1058
01:13:41,480 --> 01:13:43,610
已经成功地带着毛伊
You have officially delivered Maui.

1059
01:13:43,730 --> 01:13:45,630
跨越了整片大海
Across the great sea.

1060
01:13:47,310 --> 01:13:50,120
莫阿娜
Moana!  Moana!  Moana!

1061
01:13:50,190 --> 01:13:52,180
你好伟大
You're so amazing!

1062
01:13:53,780 --> 01:13:54,770
时间到了
It's time.

1063
01:14:13,120 --> 01:14:14,360
去拯救世界吧
Go, save the world.

1064
01:14:38,100 --> 01:14:39,090
毛伊
Maui!

1065
01:15:14,170 --> 01:15:15,160
你在干什么？
What... What are you doing?

1066
