- 我们过不去的  - 过得去
- We won't make it!  - Yes, we will!

1068
01:15:20,790 --> 01:15:21,810
- 快掉头  - 不
- Turn around!  - No!

1069
01:15:21,970 --> 01:15:23,380
- 莫阿娜，停下  - 不
- Moana, stop!  - No!

1070
01:15:52,290 --> 01:15:53,520
你还好吧？
Are you okay?

1071
01:15:55,660 --> 01:15:56,650
毛伊
Maui?

1072
01:16:04,430 --> 01:16:05,700
我说了掉头
I told you to turn back.

1073
01:16:08,610 --> 01:16:10,090
我觉得我们能过得去
I thought we could make it.

1074
01:16:10,770 --> 01:16:11,760
我们
We?

1075
01:16:13,200 --> 01:16:15,150
我觉得我能过得去
I thought I could make it.

1076
01:16:17,350 --> 01:16:18,340
我们可以修好它
We can fix it!

1077
01:16:18,450 --> 01:16:20,120
鱼钩法杖是天神做的
It was made by the Gods.

1078
01:16:20,670 --> 01:16:22,270
你不可能修得好
You can't fix it!

1079
01:16:23,130 --> 01:16:24,540
下次小心一点就好了
Next time we'll be more careful.

1080
01:16:25,350 --> 01:16:27,140
恶卡只能待在障壁岛上
Te Ka was stuck on the barrier islands.

1081
01:16:27,560 --> 01:16:28,550
它是熔岩做的
It's lava!

1082
01:16:28,570 --> 01:16:29,700
不能碰水
It can't go in the water.

1083
01:16:30,140 --> 01:16:31,130
我们可以绕路过去
We can find a way around.

1084
01:16:32,210 --> 01:16:33,200
我不会再去了
I'm not going back.

1085
01:16:34,600 --> 01:16:37,260
什么，我们还得把那颗心放回去呢
What... We still have to restore the heart.

1086
01:16:37,350 --> 01:16:38,370
我的鱼钩已经裂了
My hook is cracked.

1087
01:16:38,630 --> 01:16:40,450
再被击中一次，它就彻底毁了
One more hit and it's over.

1088
01:16:40,480 --> 01:16:42,720
毛伊，你必须归还特菲提之心
Maui, you have to restore the heart.

1089
01:16:42,760 --> 01:16:44,810
没有鱼钩法杖，我什么都做不了
Without my hook, I am nothing.

1090
01:16:44,840 --> 01:16:46,000
不是那样的
That's not true.

1091
01:16:46,030 --> 01:16:48,280
没有鱼钩法杖，我什么都做不了
Without my hook, I am nothing!

1092
01:16:58,250 --> 01:17:01,890
我们走到今天这一步，都是因为你当初偷了这颗心
We're only here because you stole the heart in the first place.

1093
01:17:04,160 --> 01:17:06,160
不，这一切都是因为大海说你
No, we're here because the ocean told you

1094
01:17:06,190 --> 01:17:07,910
与众不同，而你也就当了真
You're special and you believed it,

1095
01:17:09,810 --> 01:17:12,360
我是莫图鲁尼岛的莫阿娜
I am Moana of Motunui.

1096
01:17:12,660 --> 01:17:14,710
- 快上船，我要带你  - 再见了，莫阿娜
- You will board my boat.  - Goodbye, Moana.

1097
01:17:14,770 --> 01:17:17,320
- 跨越整片大海  - 我不能为了
- Sail across the sea,  - I'm not killing myself

1098
01:17:17,340 --> 01:17:18,930
证明自己而搭上我的性命
So you can prove you're something you're not!

1099
01:17:19,030 --> 01:17:20,660
归还特菲提之心
And restore the heart of Te Fiti!

1100
01:17:20,910 --> 01:17:22,560
大海选择了我
The Ocean chose me!

1101
01:17:24,230 --> 01:17:25,220
它选错了人
They chose wrong.

1102
01:17:35,720 --> 01:17:36,710
毛伊
Maui!

1103
01:17:51,760 --> 01:17:53,140
为什么要带我来这里
Why did you bring me here?

1104
01:17:59,020 --> 01:18:00,810
你选错了人
I'm not the right person.

1105
01:18:03,500 --> 01:18:05,910
去找个更合适的人吧
You have to choose someone else.

1106
01:18:09,060 --> 01:18:10,970
找个更合适的人
Choose someone else!

1107
01:18:12,430 --> 01:18:13,430
求你了
Please!

1108
01:18:32,740 --> 01:18:33,430
不
No.

1109
01:18:49,910 --> 01:18:52,380
你已经离家很远了
You're a long ways past the reef.

1110
01:18:53,380 --> 01:18:54,370
奶奶？
Grandma?

1111
01:18:56,680 --> 01:18:59,170
还好我选了黄貂鱼纹身
Guess I chose the right tattoo.

1112
01:19:00,280 --> 01:19:01,270
奶奶
Grandma!

1113
01:19:06,520 --> 01:19:08,020
我尽力了，奶奶
I tried, grandma.

1114
01:19:08,830 --> 01:19:09,820
可
I...

1115
01:19:10,730 --> 01:19:12,720
我做不到
I couldn't do it.

1116
01:19:13,100 --> 01:19:14,550
这不是你的错
It's not your fault.

1117
01:19:15,810 --> 01:19:18,890
我不该让你一个人承担这么多
I never should've put so much on your shoulders.

1118
01:19:20,200 --> 01:19:22,330
如果你想要回家
If you are ready to go home.

1119
01:19:23,810 --> 01:19:25,200
我可以陪你回去
I will be with you.

1120
01:19:42,470 --> 01:19:43,800
你在犹豫什么
Why do you hesitate?

1121
01:19:45,380 --> 01:19:46,370
我不知道
I don't know.

1122
01:19:50,680 --> 01:19:52,970
有个女孩多么出众
I know a girl from an island.

1123
01:19:54,010 --> 01:19:56,490
她来自那个海岛
She stands apart from the crowd.

1124
01:19:57,210 --> 01:19:59,710
她爱海洋也爱家园
She loves the sea and her people.

1125
01:20:00,410 --> 01:20:02,950
大家都为她骄傲
She makes her whole family proud.

1126
01:20:03,930 --> 01:20:06,910
也许世界和你作对
Sometimes the world seems against you.

1127
01:20:07,410 --> 01:20:10,020
旅途上跌倒受伤
The journey may leave a scar.

1128
01:20:10,480 --> 01:20:12,510
但伤疤却见证了
But scars can heal and reveal

1129
01:20:12,540 --> 01:20:15,380
你的成长
Just where you are.

1130
01:20:16,830 --> 01:20:19,540
你爱的人能改变你
The people you love will change you.

1131
01:20:20,230 --> 01:20:22,770
你学的知识指引你
The things you have learned will guide you.

1132
01:20:23,310 --> 01:20:26,130
没有什么能阻止你
And nothing on earth can silence.

1133
01:20:26,750 --> 01:20:29,680
你心中的那个声音
The quiet voice still inside you.

1134
01:20:30,130 --> 01:20:33,050
当这声音轻轻地问
And when that voice starts to whisper

1135
01:20:33,690 --> 01:20:36,060
莫阿娜，你已成长了这么多
Moana you've come so far.

1136
01:20:37,130 --> 01:20:38,550
莫阿娜，现在
Moana listen.

1137
01:20:39,020 --> 01:20:43,990
你是谁你知道吗？
Do you know who you are?

1138
01:20:45,960 --> 01:20:46,950
我是谁？
Who am I?

1139
01:20:49,440 --> 01:20:52,680
我就是我，热爱着小岛
I am a girl who loves my island.

1140
01:20:53,020 --> 01:20:55,880
这海洋给我生命
I'm the girl who loves the sea.

1141
01:20:57,340 --> 01:20:59,860
与使命
It calls me...

1142
01:21:02,450 --> 01:21:05,050
伟大的酋长是我的父亲
I am the daughter of the village chief.

1143
01:21:05,770 --> 01:21:08,920
我们的祖先越洋万里
We are descended from voyagers.

1144
01:21:09,020 --> 01:21:11,640
找到这里，然后给我
Who found their way across the world.

1145
01:21:11,850 --> 01:21:14,450
这启示
They call me ...

1146
01:21:15,600 --> 01:21:18,070
带领大家找到这地方
I've delivered us to where we are.

1147
01:21:18,800 --> 01:21:21,180
我的旅途漫长
I have journeyed farther.

1148
01:21:21,970 --> 01:21:27,720
我没有保留付出所有，但在心里
I am everything I've learned and more. Still it calls me.

1149
01:21:28,360 --> 01:21:30,820
我听到有个声音悄悄在
And the call isn't out there at all.

1150
01:21:30,850 --> 01:21:33,840
呼唤我
It's inside me.

1151
01:21:34,070 --> 01:21:40,730
像潮水涨退循环的交替
It's like the tide always falling and rising.

1152
01:21:41,180 --> 01:21:43,540
我回把你收藏在心底
I will carry you here in my heart.

1153
01:21:43,640 --> 01:21:46,680
给我提醒
You remind me.

1154
01:21:47,040 --> 01:21:49,900
路有多难
That come what may.

1155
01:21:50,050 --> 01:21:53,070
勇敢面对
I know the way!

1156
01:21:53,270 --> 01:21:57,640
我是莫阿娜
I AM MOANA!

1157
01:22:32,430 --> 01:22:34,620
我是莫图鲁尼岛的莫阿娜
I am Moana of Motunui.

1158
01:22:36,050 --> 01:22:39,420
快上船，我要带你跨越整片大海
Aboard my boat, I will sail across the sea.

1159
01:22:40,000 --> 01:22:42,480
归还特菲提之心
And restore the heart of Te Fiti.

1160
01:23:19,160 --> 01:23:21,060
恶卡不可能下到水里
Te Ka can't follow us into the water.

1161
01:23:21,860 --> 01:23:23,850
我们可以穿过障壁岛
We'll make it pass the barrier islands.

1162
01:23:24,260 --> 01:23:26,050
然后抵达特菲提
We'll make it to Te Fiti.

1163
01:23:26,150 --> 01:23:27,940
可惜你什么都听不懂
None of which you understand.

1164
01:23:28,050 --> 01:23:29,540
因为你只是一只鸡
Because you are a chicken.

1165
01:24:35,980 --> 01:24:36,970
不
No!

1166
01:24:38,080 --> 01:24:38,870
憨憨
Hei-hei!

1167
01:24:38,900 --> 01:24:40,460
不
No, no, no, no, no!

1168
01:24:42,090 --> 01:24:42,940
干得漂亮
Nice work!

1169
01:24:53,030 --> 01:24:53,860
特菲提
Te Fiti!

1170
01:25:19,400 --> 01:25:20,070
毛伊
Maui!

1171
01:25:24,790 --> 01:25:25,850
你回来了
You came back.

1172
01:25:29,820 --> 01:25:30,810
但你的鱼钩
But your hook.

1173
01:25:31,320 --> 01:25:32,850
再被击中一次就
One more hit, and ...

1174
01:25:33,630 --> 01:25:35,210
恶卡得先抓到我才行
Te Ka's gotta catch me first.

1175
01:25:38,210 --> 01:25:39,670
我来掩护你，小英雄
I got your back, chosen one.

1176
01:25:40,810 --> 01:25:41,810
去拯救世界吧
Go, save the world.

1177
01:25:42,230 --> 01:25:42,730
毛伊
Maui.

1178
01:25:43,710 --> 01:25:44,500
谢谢你
Thank you.

1179
01:25:45,690 --> 01:25:46,530
不用谢
You're welcome.

1180
01:26:20,680 --> 01:26:21,540
嘿，恶卡
Hey... Te Ka!

1181
01:26:22,970 --> 01:26:23,990
鲨鱼头
Shark head.

1182
01:26:36,800 --> 01:26:37,720
莫阿娜
Moana!

1183
01:26:47,830 --> 01:26:49,630
把那颗心放进漩涡里
Get the heart to the spiral!

1184
01:27:28,270 --> 01:27:28,960
特菲提
Te Fiti.

1185
01:27:30,260 --> 01:27:31,160
特菲提消失了
It's gone.

1186
01:27:44,420 --> 01:27:46,260
恶卡
TE KA!!

1187
01:28:22,020 --> 01:28:23,180
让她过来吧
Let her come to me.

1188
01:28:46,570 --> 01:28:50,710
走过千山与万水追寻你
I have crossed the horizon to find you.

1189
01:28:57,130 --> 01:28:59,750
我了解你
I know your name.

1190
01:29:03,590 --> 01:29:08,280
他们偷走你心底的自己
They have stolen the heart from inside you.

1191
01:29:11,970 --> 01:29:15,010
却不能够定义你
But this does not define you.

1192
01:29:18,560 --> 01:29:22,370
这不是真的你
This is not who you are.

1193
01:29:24,410 --> 01:29:29,980
你是谁，你决定
You know who you are...

1194
01:29:36,460 --> 01:29:38,540
谁才是真正的你
Who you trully are.

1195
01:30:02,400 --> 01:30:03,480
特菲提
Te Fiti.

1196
01:30:33,890 --> 01:30:34,950
小笨鸡还活着呢
The chicken lives.

1197
01:30:37,220 --> 01:30:38,920
很抱歉毁了你的鱼钩
I'm sorry about your hook.

1198
01:30:39,580 --> 01:30:44,280
其实，不管有没有鱼钩，我都是毛伊
Well, hook, no hook, I'm Maui.

1199
01:31:03,660 --> 01:31:05,200
特菲提
Te Fiti!

1200
01:31:07,900 --> 01:31:08,890
你最近好吗？
How you've been?

1201
01:31:11,720 --> 01:31:14,720
好吧，都是我的错
Look, what I did was wrong.

1202
01:31:15,920 --> 01:31:17,260
我真的很抱歉
I have no excuse.

1203
01:31:18,570 --> 01:31:19,560
对不起
I'm sorry.

1204
01:31:28,610 --> 01:31:31,460
要知道拒绝女神给的礼物可不礼貌
You know, it'd be rude to refuse a gift from a Goddess.

1205
01:31:37,170 --> 01:31:37,960
谢谢
Thank you.

1206
01:31:38,050 --> 01:31:40,560
你的宽宏大量让我不胜感激
Your kind gesture is deeply appreciated.

1207
01:32:30,680 --> 01:32:31,770
我会想你的，小笨鸡
Gonna miss you, drumstick.

1208
01:32:32,100 --> 01:32:33,470
你可以跟我们一起走
You could come with us, you know.

1209
01:32:34,070 --> 01:32:37,490
我的族人们需要寻路高手的指点
My people are going to need a master wayfinder.

1210
01:32:39,350 --> 01:32:40,460
他们已经有一位了
They already have one.

1211
01:32:59,490 --> 01:33:00,780
那就再见了，毛伊
See you out there, Maui.

1212
01:33:01,540 --> 01:33:03,610
那就再见吧，莫阿娜
See you out there, Moana...

1213
01:33:57,250 --> 01:33:58,420
妈妈，爸爸
Mom! Dad!

1214
01:33:58,700 --> 01:33:59,750
莫阿娜
Moana!

1215
01:34:08,130 --> 01:34:12,390
我可能离家稍微远了点
I may have gone a little ways past the reef.

1216
01:34:14,030 --> 01:34:15,210
这才是你
It suits you.

1217
01:34:15,780 --> 01:34:17,500
- 她回来了  - 莫阿娜
- She's back!  - Moana!

1218
01:34:18,110 --> 01:34:19,100
胖胖
Pua!

1219
01:34:21,770 --> 01:34:22,760
莫阿娜
Moana!

1220
01:35:15,540 --> 01:35:17,590
定好了目的地
We set a course to find...

1221
01:35:17,910 --> 01:35:22,480
每一次出行找寻新天地
A brand new island everywhere we roam.

1222
01:35:24,570 --> 01:35:27,100
家乡的模样放心里
We keep our island in our mind.

1223
01:35:27,440 --> 01:35:32,270
时间到了就回家，千山万水
And when it's time to find home, We know the way

1224
01:35:32,310 --> 01:35:36,830
我们去探索每一个符号
Aue, Aue. We are explorers reading every sign.

1225
01:35:36,890 --> 01:35:41,770
这里有我们的祖先，古老的故事与传承
We tell the stories of our elders in a never ending chain.

1226
01:35:48,940 --> 01:35:54,240
千山万水
We know the way....

